{"tid":1001451,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"BioHazard 2 Remake (Mr.X係諧星黎?) 集中討論區 9","createTime":"2019-01-30T07:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T13:42:41.000Z","uid":5153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"77758dc1911f2cb74d4cf803a85919c0be620c2f","tid":1001451,"uid":5153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://t00.deviantart.net/56pvoo_Ef2Lap6Phhevs4t5pDpY=/700x350/filters:fixed_height(100,100):origin()/pre00/a3f9/th/pre/f/2018/165/f/b/resident_evil_2_remake_wallpaper_hd_by_briellalove-dceckl3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft00.deviantart.net%2F56pvoo_Ef2Lap6Phhevs4t5pDpY%3D%2F700x350%2Ffilters%3Afixed_height%28100%2C100%29%3Aorigin%28%29%2Fpre00%2Fa3f9%2Fth%2Fpre%2Ff%2F2018%2F165%2Ff%2Fb%2Fresident_evil_2_remake_wallpaper_hd_by_briellalove-dceckl3.png&h=8029a9ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇黎大家都鐘意叫BIO,就用番BIO圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n注意: 呢個POST有大量痴線佬,又話要人同喪屍多P交配,又話除LEON條底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cm3ETiA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCm3ETiA.png&h=3d84562b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家生客同熟客都有得買,不過熟客可以去CAPCOM總部玩同埋會得到REMARK版遊戲</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzcZpTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzcZpTu.jpg&h=ee6a2bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS4 , XBOX , PC (STEAM)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">25/1/2019正式發售</span></strong><br />\n港行係有血腥爆頭標腸版<br />\n唔想見到就自己搵日版D版<br />\n香港大致得兩種版本<br />\n(PS4為例)<br />\n普通膠盒版<br />\nCollector box (冇四條KEY,歐美版先有)<br />\n<br />\n港行冇鐵盒版<br />\n要就搵歐美版<br />\n<br />\nRemake版LEON真人Model<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/iQ7gCaUHwoToh7dgJrvacV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net%2FiQ7gCaUHwoToh7dgJrvacV.jpg&h=f128464f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nClaire真人Model<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LepH62p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLepH62p.png&h=d10841b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DhfOq5qU8AIyyVX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDhfOq5qU8AIyyVX.jpg&h=cf0ec08f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DhfOrl7UcAAOtxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDhfOrl7UcAAOtxc.jpg&h=ba4c60dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DhfOpZiVMAA39Ux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDhfOpZiVMAA39Ux.jpg&h=13146a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAda Wong真人Model<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180105/photo/bkn-20180105135958215-0105_00862_001_10p.jpg?20180106051319\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180105135958215-0105_00862_001_10p.jpg%3F20180106051319&h=213352bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:點分日版同美版?<br />\nA:基本上係香港買到港行係雙封面,美版血腥版內容,再唔係可以睇隻BLURAY區碼 (1:歐美, 2:日本, 3:港行)<br />\n<br />\nQ:有冇中文字幕?<br />\nA:港行係有繁體中文字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同蝗語配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ:有冇表裏關之分?<br />\nA: 暫時睇上黎係有GE<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nby2mSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnby2mSw.jpg&h=d8f5897f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:有咩隱藏野玩?<br />\nA:官方公佈左有豆腐模式,第四生還者,GHOST模式,仲有PS1起角版男女主角用<br />\nPS1起角版LEON GAMEPLAY<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5chixBvWMeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5chixBvWMeg&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=253eec8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5chixBvWMeg</a><br />\n<br />\n第四生還者HUNK GAMEPLAY <span style=\"color: red;\">(嚴重劇透,心臟有毛病或孕婦請自己決定睇唔睇)</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZS87H2FmsKg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZS87H2FmsKg&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=b1f07ef7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZS87H2FmsKg</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: Mr.X點搞呀，煩過我阿媽<br />\nA: (根據巴打貓之子提供）<br />\n其實你唔跑，唔開槍，Mr. X 喺正常情況唔會跟住你<br />\n<br />\n即係一但你開完槍，再Mr. X 出場嘅音樂，就有咁快跑咁快去d 有Mr. X 頂帽嘅地方，Mr. X 唔會走入走嘅地方，你就可以慢慢觀察返Mr. X 去邊<br />\n<br />\n同理，可以用呢個方法引Mr. X 出你想去嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n另外，暫時有個場景你喺入面，Mr. X 一定會入去搵你： 洗衣房<br />\n但如果你入去係慢行，佢會喺門口望兩望就走咗去<br />\n<br />\n成就獎杯列表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Tm3F4n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Tm3F4n.png&h=14ca9405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浣熊先生全位置<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ign.com/wikis/re2-remake/Mr._Raccoon_Toy_Locations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ign.com%2Fwikis%2Fre2-remake%2FMr._Raccoon_Toy_Locations&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=29ba49b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ign.com/wikis/re2-remake/Mr._Raccoon_Toy_Locations</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由巴打讚美太陽提供</span><br />\n<br />\n其他精彩圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7dRwEz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7dRwEz.png&h=6df2050f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vnrkxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vnrkxV.png&h=3ca57532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGkMkxW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGkMkxW.png&h=aa792c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvTVdSY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvTVdSY.gif&h=eab5fb62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由巴打讚美太陽提供</span><br />\n<br />\n以下資料由天溢巴打提供:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.entertainment14.net/blog/post/110954657-%E6%83%A1%E9%9D%88%E5%8F%A4%E5%A0%A1-2-%E9%87%8D%E8%A3%BD%E7%89%88-%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5%E5%8C%AF%E9%9B%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.entertainment14.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F110954657-%25E6%2583%25A1%25E9%259D%2588%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25A0%25A1-2-%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E7%2589%2588-%25E6%2594%25BB%25E7%2595%25A5%25E5%258C%25AF%25E9%259B%2586&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=e37c54db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.entertainment14.net/blog/post/110954657-%E6%83%A1%E9%9D%88%E5%8F%A4%E5%A0%A1-2-%E9%87%8D%E8%A3%BD%E7%89%88-%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5%E5%8C%AF%E9%9B%86</a><br />\n攻略網，但建議第一次玩只睇點拎武器，享受解謎過程"},{"pid":"7b765730b112d9ce7f975c23dd7d9f6ef7dbebe3","tid":1001451,"uid":187513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DBMHqzF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDBMHqzF.gif&h=e81b4ba9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WAR4DUF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWAR4DUF.png&h=026b0131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條女好正"},{"pid":"2b50a9979d04a4527df060ab9521b8ae407e6c37","tid":1001451,"uid":58975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:34:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3df5260143c4002da90d641fad2da564f44a6184","tid":1001451,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b765730b112d9ce7f975c23dd7d9f6ef7dbebe3","tid":1001451,"uid":187513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:15:28.000